D64::Disk::Dir Version 0.03
===========================

D64::Disk::Dir is a Perl module providing an abstraction layer above
D64::Disk::Image module (Perl interface to Per Olofsson's "diskimage.c",
an ANSI C library for manipulating Commodore disk images written in C),
enabling users to handle D64 disk image directories in a higher-level
object-oriented way.

PREREQUISITES

    Array::Iterator >= 0.06
    D64::Disk::Image >= 0.01

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

